+ * Copyright 2011 Hauke Mehrtens <hauke@hauke-m.de>
+ *
+ * Derived from the OHCI-PCI driver
+ * Copyright 1999 Roman Weissgaerber
+ * Copyright 2000-2002 David Brownell
+ * Copyright 1999 Linus Torvalds
